ResponseBody:
1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:11,000
Whisper is an automatic recognition system of speech trained on 680,000 hours of multilingual and multitasking data collected on the Internet.

2
00:00:11,000 --> 00:00:20,000
We establish that the use of data of such a number and such a diversity is the reason why the system is able to understand many accents,

3
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:27,000
despite background noise, to understand technical vocabulary, and to succeed in translation from various languages into English.

4
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:33,000
As a free software, we distribute the source code for our models and for the inference,

5
00:00:33,000 --> 00:00:41,000
so that they can be used as a starting point to build useful applications and to help progress research in speech processing.
